            Build a portfolio that actually gets you hired. No theory—real data from 73 portfolio conversion tests.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm border-2 border-cyan-300 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg">
              <span class="text-cyan-600 font-black">7</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium text-sm">Builders Tested</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm border-2 border-cyan-300 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg">
